### Endpoint: Agregar Item a Pedido
POST https://localhost:{{port}}/api/orders/add-item
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "productId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "quantity": 2,
  "userId": "user123"
}

###

### Endpoint: Eliminar Item de Pedido
DELETE https://localhost:{{port}}/api/orders/1/items/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

###

### Endpoint: Cancelar Pedido
PUT https://localhost:{{port}}/api/orders/1/cancel

###

